quagga.input.subject: Re: So far
quagga.input.body:
sorry, got this too late, will be there tommorrow
bright and early( btw, u must of argued good to keep
the numbers even that good, nice going).  I'll be
there pretty early, plane lands at 9:00 will come
right in.

I'll ask for u, feel free to call me at home... 708
422 4514 if u want to talk tonight.

later

--- "Kitchen, Louise" <Louise.Kitchen@ENRON.com>
wrote:
> So far we have spent today relooking at our numbers
> for the whole business.  Technology is looking about
> the same as before (possibly 10 -  15 less in Jay's
> area).  I think it would be a good idea for you to
> come down and have dinner with either myself or
> myself, Jenny and Jay together tomorrow.  Hutch is
> coming down tomorrow night.
>
> Regards
>
> Louise
>
